陳明通今日到立法院接受質詢，國民黨立委江啟臣問及，兩岸關係惡化到連香港辦事處處長都無法就任，到底是甚麼原因，陳明通表示，目前有管道積極交涉，但不知道港府為何不發簽證，目前由香港辦事處的綜合業務組長代理高銘村處長，希望港府盡快發出簽證。陳明通又表示，駐港代表張良任曾延遲就任13個月，「我每天都在想辦法想破頭了」。<br />\n<br />\n而台經辦現時由高銘村代理處長，他早前表示希望盧長水的工作簽證「盡快可以核發」，不要影響兩地關係，但承認「現在兩岸關係未有以前哪麼好」。香港政府早前回覆查詢時就表示，入境處不會評論個別個案。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：台灣蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A88%E6%9C%88%E5%B1%A5%E6%96%B0-%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E6%83%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A88%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B1%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&d=ax1iBzcBQBHgfFlmKBArgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7162186e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A88%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B1%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&h=0f43fba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A88%E6%9C%88%E5%B1%A5%E6%96%B0-%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E6%83%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95/</a>"