a9d6","tid":871883,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce207836c824e06d91dd52be074bf8fbb3c90e60","tid":871883,"uid":60047,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"即刻停發入台證啦<br />\n駐港代表都唔批簽證<br />\n班爛鳩港豬憑咩入境<br />\n即刻譴返埋香港駐台代表<br />\n等佢咁臭串"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/195907_70cf0a913b80930a3e8c035c070110d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F195907_70cf0a913b80930a3e8c035c070110d6.png&h=edcb8374&s={SIZE}\" />懸空緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}